headline: American Tower Corporation Releases 2024 Sustainability Executive Report
summary: BOSTON, July 23, 2025--American Tower Corporation (NYSE: AMT) today announced the release of its 2024 sustainability executive report and accompanying indices and supplements, which highlight the Company’s progress across its three sustainability pillars: Environment, Social, and Governance. The report underscores American Tower’s commitment to aligning sustainability with operational excellence and long-term value creation.
